reviewText: The film quality doesn't quite showcase the beauty of Uschi, Gerri Reeves fairs a little better with less grainy film. There isn't much here but this is the way it was once. A time when we were less concerned about cosmetic enhancements and women simply had a different quality of beauty.

:) the worst the worst ever. if you are a fan of the seventies stag films as I am you will not enjoy or appreciate this disk. absolutely no attempt was made to clean up the video. do not waste your money. this is trash. the best disc I have found  is a title which includes the word sleazy and seventies. you will not regret purchasing this disk.
Never a bad idea putting nude footage of Uschi Digard in a film.

Well, I like the content, but the film transfers are horrible. I suppose I didn't expect high definition from this type of thing, but yeah, the transfers are pretty bad in a lot of cases. The music stinks too. They shouldve used something a little more burlesque, but you can always mute it.

The content however is just what is promised; no gripe there. If you're a fan of this sort of thing, you won't be disappointed.

Three stars = "its okay"
